tafsir[69]{c,v,t}:
  29,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim: yewtere sugu Й—ee Aayeeje yawtiino ka fuЙ—Й—orde cortewol (simoore)Al-Baqarah."
  29,2,"E yimЙ“e Й“en sikku, fii Й“e wi'ii: Men gomЙ—inii Alla, Й“e accirte non, hara Й“e jarribaaka, haa gomЙ—inal maЙ“Й“e ngal Й“annga tigiri? Wanaa no Й“e sikkiri non."
  29,3,"GomЙ—ii, Men jarribike Й“en adinooЙ“e Й“e. Maa Alla feГұГұinir Й“annginangol on, goonguЙ“e Й“en, e gomЙ—inal maЙ“Й“e nagl, e fende fenuЙ“e Й“en e Й—um."
  29,4,"Kaa ko ronndoriiЙ“e bone sirku ekn mun kon sikku, wonnde Й“e laawoto Men, haa Й“e daЙ—a lepte Amen? Fii Гұaawoore maЙ“Й“e nden bonii; tawde Й“e laawotaako Alla, Й“e daЙ—ataa kadi lepte Makko Й—en, si Й“e maayii e keeferaaku."
  29,5,"Kala jortiiЙ—o hawroygol e Alla Г‘alnde Darngal, fii yo O warjo mo, yo o anndu pellet, caatal(lajal) ngal Alla happi ngal fii Й—um, ko hewtawl jooni. Ko Kanko woni Nanoowo haalaaji jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, AnnduЙ—o kuuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e. Huunde laawotaako Mo e Й—um, O yoЙ“itoyay Й“e fow e mun."
  29,6,"Kala tiiЙ—niiЙ—o e dewal, o woЙ—Й—itii e geddi, o wonii fii Alla, haray ko hoore-makko o tiiЙ—nanii; tawde nafa Й—um on, ko e makko artata. Alla kan, ko yondinii- Й—o e tageefo ngon fow; dewal maЙ“Й“e Й“eydataa Mo, goopi maЙ“Й“e kadi Й—uytataa Mo."
  29,7,"ЖҒen gomЙ—imЙ“e non, Й“e muГұГұii e jarrabuyee Amen on, Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe, ma Men momtan Й“e junuubi maЙ“Й“e Й—in, Men yoЙ“itiroya Й“e laakara, ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e ko Й“e gollaynoo aduna kon."
  29,8,"Men yamirii neЙ—Й—anke on, moЖҙЖҙugol e mawЙ“e makko Й“en Й—iЙ—o. Si mawЙ“e maa Й“en arii doolude ma, fii sirkangol Lam, huunde nde a alanaa Й—um ganndal (wano ko heЙ“unoo Sa'd ibn Abi Waqqaas (yo Alla wele mo, e jurol neene makko), wata a Й—ofto Й“e e Й—um; tawde Й—oftagol alanaa tagaaЙ—o, e ka taguЙ—o On yeddetee. Ko Am tun, woni ruttorde mon, Г‘alnde Darngal, Mi yeetitoo on, kon ko gollaynoЙ—on aduna, Mi yoЙ“ita on Й—um."
  29,9,"ЖҒen gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla, Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe, ma Men waЙ—tiduЙ“e e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en, Г‘alnde Darngal. Men mooЙ“ida Й“e, kadi, Men yoЙ“ida Й“e fow nde wootere."
  29,10,"Hino e yimЙ“e Й“en, wi'oowo: Men gomЙ—inii Alla; hara non, si heeferЙ“e Й“en lorrii mo fii gomЙ—inal makko ngal, o waЙ—iray lorra maЙ“Й“e kan, wano lepte Alla Й—en, o murta e gomЙ—inal. Si ballal kadi immorii ka Joomi maa, an NulaaЙ—o, pellet, Й“e wi'ay: MeЙ—en wondunoo e mo'on, onon muumini'en. Kere wanaa Alla Й“uri anndude ko woni e Й“erЙ—e yimЙ“e Й“en? Huunde suuЙ—aaki Mo e ko woni e majje, foti ko keeferaaku maa gomЙ—inal. Ko honno Й“e yeetorta Alla, fii ko woni e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, ka tawata Himo Й“uri Й“e anndude Й—um?"
  29,11,"Ma Alla feГұГұin fii gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en tigiri, ma O feГұГұin kadi fii naafiqiiЙ“e yaltinayЙ“e gomЙ—inal Й“en, Й“e suuЙ—a keeferaaku ngun."
  29,12,"HeeferЙ“e Й“en wi'ani gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla Й“en: Jokkee diina amen kan, men fawtoto fii junuubi mon Й—in; hara ko menen ronnditotoo fii majji. Kono Й“e wonaali fawtotooЙ“e hay huunde e junuubi maЙ“Й“e. Pellet, ko Й“e fenuЙ“e e kan haala maЙ“Й“e."
  29,13,"Kono Й“ee sirkooЙ“e noddooЙ“e e meere maЙ“Й“e nden, ko maa Й“e fawtoo fii junuubi maЙ“Й“e Й—i faggitii Й—in, e junuubi kala jokkuЙ—o Й“e, e hoore junuubi Й“en Й—on Й—in ustetaake. Ko maa kadi Й“e lamndoyee Г‘alnde Darngal, gaay e kon ko Й“e faggitotonoo e meereeji ka aduna."
  29,14,"GomЙ—ii Men nulii Nuuhu e yimЙ“e makko Й“en, o ГұiiЙ“i hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, duuЙ“i teemeЙ—Й—e jeenay e cappanЙ—e jowi, himo nodaa Й“e e wootinЙ—ingol Alla. Kono Й“e fenni mo, Й“e lutti e keeferaaku; waame on nanngi Й“e, hari ko Й“e tooГұirЙ“e yeddugol Alla, e fennugol NulaaЙ—o Makko on, Й“e halkiraa yoolagol."
  29,15,"Men daЙ—ndi Nuuhu yooloragol halakuyee, e gomЙ—imЙ“e wondunooЙ“e e makko Й“en ka laana; Men waЙ—i laana kan, waajitorka yimЙ“e Й“en."
  29,16,"An NulaaЙ—o, janto kadi fillayee Ibraahiima on, nde o wi'annoo yimЙ“e makko Й“en: rewee Alla tun, huliron lepte Makko Й—en, Й—oftagol yamirooje Makko Й—en, woЙ—Й—itoo haЙ—aaЙ—i Makko Й—in; ko Й—um Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on, si wonii hiЙ—on anndi."
  29,17,"Anndee ko rewoton kon, onon Й“ee sirkooЙ“e, ko sanamuuji Й—i nafataa Й—i loraataa, hiЙ—on taЖҙa fenaande, aaЖҙagol wonnde hiЙ—i hanndi e reweede. Pellet, Й—in Й—i rewoton gaani Alla, Й—i waawaa on arsikude, sakko Й—i waЙ—a Й—um; awa Й—aЙ“Й“iree arsike on ka Alla, tawde ko Kanko woni arsikoowo On, rewon Mo Kanko tun, yettiron Mo neema arsike on. Ko ka Makko tun, woni ruttorde mon, Г‘alnde Darngal, fii hasbeede yoЙ“itee, wanaa ka sanamuuji mon."
  29,18,"Si onon Й“ee sirkooЙ“e on fennii ko Muhammadu (jom kisiyee) addi kon, haray mofte adinooЙ“e on kadi feenniino Nuuhu e 'Adi e Samuuda e woЙ—Й“e goo. Alaa ko fawii e NulaaЙ—o on, si wanaa yottingol Й“anngina. GomЙ—ii le o yottinii e mo'on, ko Joomi makko nuli mo e mon kon."
  29,19,"E Й“ee fennooЙ“e yi'aali no Alla fuЙ—Й—orta non tagu ngun, refti O ruttitay ngu Й“aawo fii maggu gasude? Pellet, Й—um ko ko newanii Alla. Ko O hattanЙ—o, Mo huunde ronkintaa Mbo."
  29,20,"An NulaaЙ—o, maakan Й“ee fennuЙ“e ummital: yiilee ka leydi, taskoЙ—on no Alla fuЙ—Й—ori tagu ngun. Refti Alla wuurnitay yimЙ“e Й“en, e nguurndam goo, fii hasbeede. Pellet, Alla ko hattanЙ—o kala huunde. Huunde ronkintaa Mo. Wanaa wuurnitugol yimЙ“e Й“en, wano woniri non, O ronkaano tagugol Й“e ka arannde."
  29,21,"Himo leptira nunЙ—al Makko ngal, mo O muuyani e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, O yurminira Й“ural Makko ngal, mo O muuyani e maЙ“Й“e. Ko ka Makko tun, woni ruttorde mon, Г‘alnde Darngal, fii hasbeede, Й“aawo immitineede e genaale mon."
  29,22,"On wonaali laawotooЙ“e Joomi mon, wanaa Й“occittooЙ“e lepte Makko Й—en ka leydi, wanaa ka kammu; alanaa on kadi, gaanin Alla giЙ—o heftoowo fii mon, wanaa ballo duГұanayЙ—o on lepte Makko Й—en."
  29,23,"ЖҒen yedduЙ“e Aayeeje Alla Й—en, e hawroygol e Makko ngol Г‘alnde Darngal, Й“en taЖҙike e yurmeende Am, tawde Й“e naatataa Aljanna poomaa, sabu keeferaaku maЙ“Й“e ngun. ЖҒen Й—on, hino woodani Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e, haЙ“Й“itiiЙ—e Й“e ka laakara."
  29,24,"Nde Annabi Ibraahiima waajinoo yimЙ“e makko Й“en rewugol Alla tun, tertoo sanamu, jaabawol maЙ“Й“e ngol wonaano, si wanaa wiide Й“e: waree mo, maa bugoЙ—on mo kaa yiite, no daЙ—ndiron reweteeЙ—i mon Й—in. Kono Alla hisini mo e ngen yiite. Pellet, wonii ngon tottirgol e yiite, Й“aawoo bugeede e magge, tasakuyee, wonannde yimЙ“e gomЙ—imЙ“e, tawde ko Й“en Й—on tun waajitorta."
  29,25,"Annabi Ibraahiima maaki: anndee ko rewoton kon gaanin Alla, ko sanamuuji, Й—i rewirton, fii yiЙ—indirgol hakkunde mon, ka nguurndam aduna. Hooti non, Г‘alnde Darngal, ngol giggol taЖҙoyay hakkunde mon, woЙ—Й“e e mon yeddoya Й“eya, tuma lepte Й—en feeГұata, Й“eya kadi huЙ—oya Й“eya, hara non, jaaЖҙorde mon on fow, ko ka Yiite, ka on alaa wallooЙ“e e Й—en lepte Alla, gile e sanamuuji mon Й—i rewaynoЙ—on Й—in, wanaa fere goЙ—Й—um goo."
  29,26,"Annabi Luutu gomЙ—ini mo. Annabi Inraahiima maaki: Min on, ko mi feroowo ka Joomi am, e leydi Saami barkinaandi ndin. Ko Kanko woni FooluЙ—o Mo fooletaake, Mo hoynataa feruЙ—o ka Makko, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o e eЙ“Й“oore Mun, e toppitannde Mun."
  29,27,"men yeЙ—i Ibraahiima Ishaaqa, e geЙ—al makko Yaaquuba, Men waЙ—i e geyngol makko ngol, Annabaaku e Deftere jipponriinde ka Alla. Men okki mo mbarjaari muГұal makko ngal e hoore goonga ka aduna, moЖҙЖҙugol geyngol e mantoore labaande. Kanko on ka laakara, pellet, ko o yoЙ“oyteeЙ—o njoЙ“di moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en, hara njoЙ“di makko aduna ndin Й—uytetaake e ndi laakara ndin."
  29,28,"Janto kadi, an NulaaЙ—o, Luutu, tuma nde o maakannoo yimЙ“e makko Й“en: ""E on waЙ—ay pankare Й—e gooto e winndere nden adaaki on e mun? Ko onon adii sincude koo ko haqqil hisuki salotoo."
  29,29,"E on aray yottoragol e worЙ“e Й“en ka duburi maЙ“Й“e, fii ittugol tuuyo? SakkoЙ—on seteeЙ“e Й“en ka laawi, haa Й“e acca feЖҙЖҙirde Й—on, sabu hulugol pankare mon? Huuwon e mbatirdu mon ndun piiji aГұiniiЙ—i, wano wirtere e lorrirgol feЖҙЖҙooЙ“e konngol e kuugal? Kono jaabawol yimЙ“e makko Й“en wonaano, si wanaa wiide Й“e: awa addan men lepte Alla Й—en Й—e hulЙ“inirtaa men, si tawii ko a jeyaaЙ—o e goonguЙ“e Й“en."
  29,30,"Annabi Luutu torii Joomi mun, Й“aawo yoorere hoore yimЙ“e makko Й“en, nde Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“irnoo mo addangol Й“e lepte Й—en, o maaki: Joomi am, wallam e hoore yimЙ“e bonnirooЙ“e ka leydi Й“en, saakitugol keeferaaku e piiji kaanuЙ—i."
  29,31,"Tuma nde Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“e Men immini Й“en addannoo Ibraahiima welo-welo jibingol Ishaaqa e geЙ—al on Й—on, woni Yaaquuba, Й“e wi'ani mo: menen, ko men halkooЙ“e yimЙ“e ndee Saduum, saare Luutu nden.Tawde pellet, yimЙ“e mayre laatike tooГұirooЙ“e kuuЙ—e pankare."
  29,32,"Annabai Ibraahiima maakani Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en: kono Luutu no e nden saare, nde faalaЙ—on halkude. O tawaaka le e tooГұuЙ“e Й“en. Malaa'ika'en jaabii: ko menen Й“uri anndude fii wonЙ“e ton. Ma men daЙ—ndu mo halkagol, kanko e Й“eynguure makko nden, si wanaa debbo makko on, o jeyaama e heddotooЙ“e e hlakaare nden, men waЙ—tiday mo e maЙ“Й“e."
  29,33,"Nde Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en immini halkugol yimЙ“e Luutu Й“en hewtunoo ka Luutu, o saЙ—tiraa fii maЙ“Й“e, arugol maЙ“Й“e ngol sunini mo, sabu ko jiiЙ“odu ndu o anndiri yimЙ“e makko Й“en. Tawde Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en ardirii mbaadi worЙ“e, yimЙ“e makko Й“en non, ko ittirayЙ“e tuuyu mun e worЙ“e tun. Kono Malaa'ika'en jaabii mo: wata a hulu, Й“e hewtirtaa ma bone, wata a suno kadi e ko men humpitirmaa halkugol Й“e ngol; men daЙ—ndete an e Й“eynguure maa nden, si wanaa debbo maa on, o jeyaama e heddotooЙ“e e halkaare nden, men waЙ—tiday mo e maЙ“Й“e."
  29,34,"Ko men jippinooЙ“e lepte e yimЙ“e ndee saare, huuwooЙ“e jiiЙ“oldu, immorde ka kammu, woni kaaЖҙe immorЙ—e ""Sijjiil"", sabu ko Й“e yaltunoo e Й—oftaare kon: hiЙ“e faggitoo pankare bonЙ—e, anndiranooЙ“e ittugol tuuyo mun e worЙ“e Й“en, acca Й—on rewЙ“e Й“en."
  29,35,"GomЙ—ii Men accii e nden saare nden Men halki, maande Й“anngunde, wonannde yimЙ“e haqqilooЙ“e Й“en. Tawde ko Й“en Й—on waajitorta maandeeji Й—in."
  29,36,"Men nuli kadi e Madyana, musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e on ka dammbe, Annabi Shu'aybu. O maaki: ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, rewee Alla tun, jortoron dewal mon ngal, mbarjaari Г‘alaande sakkitiinde nden, wata on wonir e leydi ndin, gollugol bone saakita Й—um."
  29,37,"YimЙ“e makko Й“en fenni mo. Dillaanngo ngon nanngi Й“e, Й“e waЙ—tini ka koЙ—ooli maЙ“Й“e, ko Й“e yanirЙ“e geece maЙ“Й“e, moddirЙ“e loope ka geece, Й“e waawaa memminaade."
  29,38,"Men halki kadi Aadi'en, yimЙ“e Huudu Й“en, e Samuuda'en, yimЙ“e Saalih Й“en. GomЙ—ii Й“annganii on, onon yimЙ“e Makka Й“en, fii galleeji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, Hegra e Ash-ShiД§r (e nder diiwal Hadramawt ngal), Hajri seeditiЙ—on ko tinndinta e ko Men halkunooЙ“e kon, tawde koЙ—ooli maЙ“Й“e Й—in wontii caabeeji. Seytaane cuЙ—inan Й“e, kuuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e keeferaaku ekn, o yilti Й“e e laawol focciingol ngol, tawi le, hiЙ“e senndidniri goonga kan e majjere nden, peewal ngal e bewre nden, tippude e ko NulaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e anndini Й“e. Kono Й“e suЙ“ii jokkugol mbeleeЙ—e Й—en, Й“e acca peewal ngal."
  29,39,"Men halki kadi Qaaruuna, mutindinirgol mo e suudu makko ndun, nde o bewunoo e yimЙ“e Muusaa Й“en. Men Halkidi kadi Fir'awna e jaagorЙ—o makko on Haaruuna, yoolugol Й“e ka maayo. GomЙ—ii le, Muusaa addaniino Й“e Aayeeje Й“annguЙ—e, tinndinayЙ—e wonnde ko e goonga o woni. Kono Й“e townitorii e leydi Misra ndin, salagol gomЙ—inde mo. Kono Й“e wonaano laawotooЙ“e lepte Amen Й—en."
  29,40,"Men leptiri kala jantaaЙ“e dow Й“en, halkugol Й“e: no e maЙ“Й“e, yimЙ“e Luutu Й“en, Й“e Men wuurti kaaЖҙe sijjiila e maЙ“Й“e; no e maЙ“Й“e kadi, yimЙ“e Saalih e Shu'aybu Й“en, Й“e Men halkiri haacaango; no e maЙ“Й“e, Qaaruuna, mo Men mutindini e galle mun Й—en; no e maЙ“Й“e kadi, yimЙ“e Nuuhu Й“en e Fir'awna e Haamaana, Й“e halkiri yoolagol. Kono non, Alla siforaali tooГұirЙ—o Й“e halkirgol junuubi Й—i Й“e faggitaaki; si ko woni, ko kamЙ“e tooГұirnoo ko'e maЙ“Й“e, faggitagol geddi, haa Й“e hanndi e lepte."
  29,41,"Misal sirkooЙ“e jogitiiЙ“e gaanin Alla Й“en sanamuuji reweteeЙ—i, jortagol nafa e tefoore majji, ko wano misal marijaawowal saccungal suudu ka daЙ—ndira jaggitere. Ko Й“uri non lo'ude e cuuЙ—i Й—in, ko suudu marijaawo; tawde ndu dartotaako gaГұo. Ko non sanamuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—in kadi wa'i, ko nafataa, Й—i lorrataa, Й—i tefataa. Kono ko si sirkooЙ“e Й“en anndayno Й—um, si Й“e aЙ—itoo jogitorgol sanamuuji Й—in, reweteeЙ—i gaanin Alla."
  29,42,"Pellet, Alla ko annduЙ—o kon ko Й“e rewata ko woori Mo. Hunnde e mun suuЙ—aaki Mo. Ko Kanko woni FooluЙ—o Mo fooletaake, Г‘eeГұo e tagu Mun e eЙ“Й“oore Mun e toppitagol Mun."
  29,43,"ЖҠee ko mise Й—e Men piyanta yimЙ“e Й“en, fii ko finndina Й“e holla Й“e goonga, fewna Й“e e mun. Ko woni tun, taskortaako Й—e no haaniri, si wanaa annduЙ“e sari'a e ГұeГұal Alla ngal."
  29,44,"Alla tagirii kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, e hoore goonga. Wanaa e meere maa fii fijindaaru O tagiri Й—i. Pellet, wonii e ngol tagugol Й—on, tinndinoore kattal ngal, fewtiniraande gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, tawde ko kamЙ“e dallinorta tagu Alla ngun, wiide taguЙ—o On no woodaa. HeeferЙ“e Й“en kan, Й“e yawtay e Й—en tinndinooje ka Winndere e hoore-maЙ“Й“e tigiri, kono Й“e ronka waЙ—tannde yiila, e mawngu taguЙ—o On, e kattal Makko, Kanko seniiЙ—o On."
  29,45,"An NulaaЙ—o, janngan yimЙ“e Й“en, kon ko Alla wahayini e maaЙ—a ka Alqur'aanaare, ГұiiЙ“niraa julde nden no timmiri. Pellet, julde timmunde sartiiji nden, hinde haЙ—a juuluЙ—o nden, yanugol e geddi e ko aГұinii; tawde Й—um no ndaygina Й“erЙ—e Й—en, haЙ—a Й—e faggitagol geddi, Й—owa Й—e e golle moЖҙЖҙe. Faamee ko jantagol Alla ngol, Й“uri kala huunde mawnude. Alla no anndi ko golloton kon. Huunde e golle mon, suuЙ—aaki Mo. O yoЙ“itoyay on e Й—um: woni ko moЖҙЖҙere maa bone."
  29,46,"Onon gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, wata on yewtir Alyahuuda e Annasaara wennjirgol Й“e, si wanaa noone Й“urЙ—o moЖҙЖҙude on; on woni noddirgol Й“e waaju e hujjaaji Й“annguЙ—i, si wanaa hara ko Й“en tooГұirЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e sattere-noppi e mawnitaare, Й“e Й“annginani on hare. ЖҒen Й—on, haЙ“ee Й“e haa Й“e silma maa Й“e jonnira sagalle Й—en junngu e junngo hara ko Й“e jaasuЙ“e. Wi'anon Alyahuuda e Annasaara: Men gomЙ—inii nden Alqur'aanaare nde Alla jippini e amen, e Й—en Й—e O jippini e mooЙ—on immorde e Tawreeta e Linjiila. ReweteeЙ—o amen On e rewteeЙ—o mon On ko gooto Mo alaa kafidiiЙ—o e Reweede Mun e Jeygol Mun e timmal Mun. Menen on, ko Kanko tun men jebbilantoo."
  29,47,"Ko wano Men jippinirnoo Defte Й—en non e Й“en adi- adinooЙ“e ma, Men jippiniri Alqur'aana e maaЙ—a. Yoga e Й“ee janngooЙ“e Tawreeta, wano вҖҳAbduLlaah ibn Salaam, hino gomЙ—iniri nde sabu ko nde joopa joopaa fii mun kon ka defte maЙ“Й“e. Yeddataa Aayeeje Amen Й—en, si wanaa heeferЙ“e Й“en woowuЙ“e yeddugol goonga ko o feeГұi woo."
  29,48,"A wonaano an NulaaЙ—o, hiЙ—a janngaynoo deftere woo, ado Alque'aana. A wonaano kadi windiray-nooЙ—o huunde Гұaamo maa ngon; tawde a janngaano. Sinno hiЙ—a janngunoo waawuЙ—aa winndugol, pellet, yimЙ“e majjuЙ“e Й“en sikkitotono Annabaaku maa ngun, Й“e dallinora wonnde ko e defte adinooЙ—e Й—en eggu-Й—aa."
  29,49,"Si ko woni fii Alqur'aana jippinaande nden e maaЙ—a, ko nde Aayeeje Й“annguЙ—e e Й“erЙ“e Й“en okkaaЙ“e ganndal e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en. Yeddataa Aayeeje Amen Й—en, si wanaa Й“en tooГұirЙ“e ko'e-mun yeddugol Alla e sirkangol Mo."
  29,50,"SirkooЙ“e Й“en wi'i: Hanno jippinee e Muhammadu maandeeji immorde ka Joomi makko sugu Й—en jippinooЙ—e e NulaaЙ“e adinooЙ“e mo Й“en? Maakan an NulaaЙ—o: Anndee maandeej Й—in, ko e JuuЙ—e Alla woni. Himo jippina Й—i nde O muuyi woo, wanaa min Й—um wonani. Min on, ko mi jertinoowo on e lepte Alla Й—en, Й“annguЙ—o jertinol."
  29,51,"Kere yonaaЙ“e Й“ee lanndiiЙ“e maandeeji wonnde Men jippinii e maaЙ—a an NulaaЙ—o, Alqur'aana hinde janngee e maЙ“Й“e? Wonii e Alqur'anaa jippinaande nden e maЙ“Й“e, yurmeende e waaju wonannde yimЙ“e gomЙ—inooЙ“e; ko kamЙ“e woni ko nafitorta ko woni e mayre. Men jippinanii Й“e ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude ko Й“e lanndii kon haa hewta ko jippinanoo e NulaaЙ“e Й“en kon."
  29,52,"Maakan Й“e an NulaaЙ—o: Alla yonii seedee goongugol ko mi addi kon, e wonnde on fennii Й—um. Himo anndi kon ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi, huunde suuЙ—aaki Mo e Й—in Й—iЙ—i. ЖҒen non gomЙ—imЙ“e meere immorde e rewooЙ“e ko wanaa Alla Й“en, Й“e yeddi Alla hannduЙ—o e reweede On tun, ko Й“en woni sooyuЙ“e Й“en; sabu koЙ“e waЙ—titiri keeferaaku ngun kon gomЙ—inal ngal."
  29,53,"ЖҒee sirkooЙ“e no hawjirane an NulaaЙ—o, lepte Й—e jertinir-Й—aa Й“e e mun Й—en. Si wanaa fii Alla hoddiranii leptugol Й“e ngol lajal ngal aditotaako ngal nennotaako, pellet, Й—en lepte Й—e Й“e hawri arayno e maЙ“Й“e. ЖҠe ardirayno Й“e juhal, hara Й“e habbanooki Й—e."
  29,54,"HiЙ“e hawjirane Й—en lepte Й—e jertinir-Й—aa Й“e, hara non pellet, Jahannama mo Alla kammbirani heeferЙ“e Й“en, ko fiiltiinge Й“e. ЖҒe hattanoytaa dokde lepte magge Й—en."
  29,55,"Г‘alnde lepte Й—en suddiroyta Й“e senngo dow maЙ“Й“e, Й—e wonta ndaЙ—Й—udi maЙ“Й“e ka ley koyЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, Alla daalana Й“e: MeeЙ—ee njoЙ“di ko gollaynoЙ—on kon immorde e sirku e goopi."
  29,56,"Ko onon yo jeyaaЙ“e Am gomЙ—imЙ“e Lam! Feree iwon e leydi ndi on waawataa rewude lam, tawde pellet, leydi Am ndin ko yaajundi. Rewee Lam Min tun, wata on kafidam(renndinam) e goЙ—Й—o goo!"
  29,57,"Wata kulol maayde haЙ—u on ferugol. Kala wnkii meeЙ—ay maayde. Refti ko ka Amen tun rutteteЙ—on Г‘alnde Darngal fii hasbeede yoЙ“ee."
  29,58,"ЖҒen gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe Й“allinayЙ—e e Alla, ma Men hoЙ—nu Й“e ka Aljanna e cuuЙ—i Й—i canЙ—i ilata senngo ley kuЙ“eeje majji, ko Й“e duumo- tooЙ“e ton poomaa, Й“e maayataa ton haa pooma, kuuЙ“al woodantaaЙ“e toon Iskin moЖҙЖҙe- re njoЙ“di gollirnooЙ“e Й—oftagol Alla Й“en."
  29,59,"Heskey moЖҙЖҙere njoЙ“di Й“en gollirЙ“e Й—oftagol Alla, muГұГұiiЙ“e e Й—oftagol Mo haЙ—itoo e yeddugol Mo, fawii Й“e e Joomi maЙ“Й“e tun e kala fiyaaku maЙ“Й“e."
  29,60,"Kala ruugayЙ—i Й—in, no Й—i foti e waade, Й—e gaynataa mooЙ“ude arsike majji wanaa fii yooЙ“agol mo. Ko Alla arsikata O arsika on. Haray ngantoo alanaa on e ronkude ferde fii kulol heege. Ko Kanko woni Nanoowo haalaaji mon, AnnduЙ—o annuyeeji e golle mon. Huunde suuЙ—aaki Mo e Й—um. Ma on yoЙ“itoy on e Й—um."
  29,61,"Pellet, si an NulaaЙ—o a lanndike Й“ee sirkooЙ“e: Ko hommbo tagi kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, O eltiri naange ngen e lewru waylondirgol? Ma Й“e wi'u: Ko Alla tagi Й—i. Ko honno non Й“e ferlitortee e gomЙ—in- gol Alla tun haa tawa Й“e reway ko nafataa lorrataa?"
  29,62,"Alla no yaГұГұana arsike on Mo O muuyi e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, O Й“illana on Mo O muuyi. O waЙ—ira Й—um ГұenЖҙal Makko ngal O anndi Kanko. Pellet, Alla ko AnnduЙ—o kala huunde. Huunde suuЙ—aaki Mo e ko moЖҙЖҙani jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en."
  29,63,"Pellet, si an NulaaЙ—o a lanndike Й“ee sirkooЙ“e: Ko hommbo jippiniri ndiyam ka kammu, O wuurnitiri Й—am leydi ndin Й“aawo ndi yoorunoo? Ma Й“e wi'u: Ko Alla jippini Й—am, O wuurnitiri Й—am leydi ndin. Maakan Й“e an NullaЙ—o: Yettoore woodanii Alla, On Й“annginЙ—o hujja e mooЙ—on. Si ko woni, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e haqqiltaa; tawde si Й“e hakkilay-noo, Й“e kafidataano e Alla Й—in sanamuuji Й—i nafataa Й—i lorrataa."
  29,64,"ЖҠam nguurndam aduna e ko woni e majjam immorde e tuuyo e dakamme wonaali, si wanaa ko mbeleeЙ—e e fijindaaru Й“erЙ—e yowitiiЙ“e e majjam. ЖҠum ko ko lannata heГұa. Pellet non, ko hoЙ—o laakara ngon woni nguurndam Й—am tigi, tawde Й—am heddotoo. Sinno Й“e annduno, Й“e ardintaano ko lannata kon yeeso ko lannataa kon."
  29,65,"Si Й“e waЙ—Й—ike ka laana, Й“e noddira Alla laЙ“Й“inan- gol Mo Kanko tun noddaandu ndun, no O daЙ—ndira Й“e e yoolagol. Tuma nde O daЙ—ndi Й“e e ngol yoolo- gol, Й“e waЙ—ta kafidude Mo e reweteeЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in."
  29,66,"ЖҒe waЙ—ti sirkude no Й“e yeddira ko Men okki Й“e kon e neemaaji, awa yo Й“e dakmitor ko Men okki Й“e kon e neweende aduna; ar ma Й“e annda battane bonnere maЙ“Й“e nden tuma Й“e maayata."
  29,67,"E yedduЙ“e neemaaji Alla Й—in e dow maЙ“Й“e tuma Alla daЙ—ndunooЙ“e yoolagol Й“en yi'aali neemaaji goo? ЖҠin woni: Wonnde Men waЙ—anii Й“e hormorde hoolniinde ka Й“e daЙ—ndata ЖҙiiЖҙe maЙ“Й“e e jawle maЙ“Й“e? Ka tawata woЙ—Й“e goo hino yoolora ka woniri, Й“en no waree dahee, rewЙ“e e Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e hoynee, jawle maЙ“Й“e ciifee(bifte)? E ko reweteЙ—i maЙ“Й“e meerente Й—in Й—i Й“e aaЖҙorta woni ko Й“e gomЙ—inta Й“e yedda neemaaji Alla Й—in Й“e ronka yettude Alla e majji?"
  29,68,"Alaa Й“urЙ—o tooГұirde wa on fefindiiЙ—o fenaande e hoore Alla o dammbira sirku e Makko, maa o fenna goonga ka NulaaЙ—o Makko on addi kan. Sikke alaa wonnde ko Jahannama woni hoЙ—orde yedduЙ“e Й“en e nanndo maЙ“Й“e."
  29,69,"ЖҒen tiiЙ—norЙ“e wonkiiji mun fii weltinirgol Men, ma Men hawrindin Й“e e peewal laawol Amen focciingol ngol.Ko pellet, Alla no wonndi e moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en ballal, e peewal."
